name.k: A Way To Smash: 3D Logic Fight
A WAY TO SMASH : Smart Fights

platformAttributes.ios.subtitle.k: A mix of puzzles and fighting!

platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: 這個遊戲將殘酷的打鬥與解謎類挑戰合而為一。如要獲勝，就需要精準地推測出每一步的動作，並在不被擊中的情況下擊潰敵人。
We love the blend of brutal brawls with puzzle-like challenges, where victory requires figuring out precisely the right series of moves to smash foes without getting hit.
